flowchart TB
    classDef st fill:#3a2a4a,stroke:#c48cff,color:#e9daff
    classDef io fill:#2a2a4a,stroke:#7e74c4,color:#dcd6f7
    classDef bad fill:#2a1d1d,stroke:#b8634a,color:#f1ddd5

    Start([User message]):::io --> Intent[Intent Classifier]:::st
    Intent -->|search| SearchSt[Search State]:::st
    Intent -->|buy| BuySt[Buy State]:::st
    Intent -->|support| SupSt[Support State]:::st

    SearchSt --> Tool1[Tool: web_search]:::st
    BuySt --> Tool2[Tool: create_order]:::st
    SupSt --> Tool3[Tool: open_ticket]:::st

    Tool1 --> Reply[Reply State]:::st
    Tool2 --> Reply
    Tool3 --> Reply

    SearchSt -.-> Escape{HITL review}:::bad
    BuySt -.-> Escape
    Reply --> Done([Reply to user]):::io
